## TRADING RULES (Learned from Live Sessions)

1. **Never let a winner become a loser** — trail stop above entry the moment you're in profit
2. **Spot for thesis plays, perps for short-term** — no leverage on 6-12 week conviction plays
3. **The lag trade** — quality tokens flat/red on green day often catch up hardest
4. **Never buy at resistance** — wait for confirmed 15m candle CLOSE above, or pullback to support
5. **RSI > 80 Howrie triangle = momentum confirmation** (not warning) WHEN volume also present
6. **Red band = exit immediately** — no hoping, no holding, click the button
7. **Stop-to-liq gap must be adequate** — at 20x keep ≥ 1% of price between stop and liq
8. **Never deploy more than 80% of margin** — keep 20% reserve minimum
9. **NEVER add to a losing position** — even with blue Howrie band. Cut losers, add to winners
10. **50% daily target = discipline** — when up 50% on the day, protect it. Don't give it back
11. **Relative weakness signal** — token flat/red while sector is green = either lag trade OR genuine weakness. Check volume and Howrie to tell the difference
12. **The funding hold** — negative funding means you RECEIVE as long. Calculate payment vs risk before closing

